title: Valery Strypeykis
text:
Valery Strypeykis (; ; born 13 November 1974) is a retired <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er. His latest club was <a href="FC%20Miory">Miory</a> in 2012. Between 2013 and 2016 he managed <a href="FC%20Naftan%20Novopolotsk">Naftan Novopolotsk</a>.
